  "page": "Andrew Tollett",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tollett\" title=\"House Tollett\"><img alt=\"House Tollett.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/50px-House_Tollett.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/75px-House_Tollett.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/100px-House_Tollett.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Andrew Tollett</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tollett\" title=\"House Tollett\"><img alt=\"House Tollett.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/50px-House_Tollett.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/75px-House_Tollett.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b1/House_Tollett.svg/100px-House_Tollett.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Winds_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tollett\" title=\"House Tollett\">House Tollett</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i> <a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Andrew Tollett </b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tollett\" title=\"House Tollett\">House Tollett</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Winds_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His relation to the head of the House, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Tollett\" title=\"Uthor Tollett\">Uthor Tollett</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tollett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tollett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Andrew attends the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> to select the members of the newly-created <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a>. During the feast, Andrew is among the young knights who dance with <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Winds_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Winds-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrew_Tollett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Winds-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Winds_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Winds_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Winds_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Alayne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Alayne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404230929\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.250 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 407/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2375/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6569/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 743/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: